window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Even heroes stumble when walking the Path of Ascension. </b></p> <p>After the excitement of the midterms has died down, both Alex and J are looking forward to their vacation. The happiness they find is all too fleeting. Alex is whisked off in the middle of the night, heading for a series of challenges that will push him to his very limits. J accepts his new role as an eager student...until he's forced to contend with a rival from his past.&nbsp;</p> <p>Can the two overcome their mounting obstacles and emerge as heroes of Ascension?&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Wyvern Academy is a harem cultivation series inspired by Japanese Light Novels as well as a deep love and respect for anime, kung fu, martial arts, and battle academy adventures. It contains some explicit adult content, unconventional relationships, and violence.</i></p>"; 
